    "Another key question was how GPT-4's performance compared to human inter-annotator agreement for that dataset.",
    "This is important as a baseline: if human agreement is low, then it is unreasonable to expect GPT-4's performance to be very high.",
    "Here, the most comparable measure was leave-one-out inter-annotator agreement, 9 which calculates the correlation between each human's ratings and the mean ratings of all other human participants (excluding the participant in question).",
